accessibility.text: You shake your head hard and try to clear up the messy mind. \"Alright,\" you talk to yourself, \"Let's think about it.\"
\"I just woke up on a great green plain without any memory.\"
\"I don't know my identity, my past, or my destination.\"
\"It seems that I am a twenties female, physically.\"
\"I'm feeling well now, not hungry, not exhausted, just confused.\"
\"So obviously my first goal for now is to find out at least one answer of my question list.\"
\"Should I stay here waiting for something to happen or choose a direction and explore?\"
